<section xml:id="algorithm-analysis_programming-exercises">
        <title>Programming Exercises</title>
        <p><ol label="1">
            <li>
                <p>Devise an experiment to verify that the vector index operator is
                    <m>O(1)</m></p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Devise an experiment to verify that find and insert are
                    <m>O(1)</m> for hash tables.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Devise an experiment that compares the performance of the <c>erase()</c>
                    operator on vectors and hash tables.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Given an array of numbers in random order, write an algorithm that works in <m>O(n\log(n))</m>
                    to find the kth smallest number in the array.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Can you improve the algorithm from the previous problem to be linear? Explain.</p>
            </li>
        </ol></p>
    </section>

